from @reallyicetomeetyou - 𝕁 𝕦 𝕟 𝕘 𝕝 𝕖  𝔹 𝕚 𝕣 𝕕

First seen @the_cocktail_bible I decided to mix this up for my wife and I as a summer sipper as we approach 90 degrees in Columbus, Ohio. Specs were modified ever so slightly based on what we had available, so be sure to head over to @highproofpreacher to see his original post/recipe. 

▫️1 oz Smith & cross
▫️.5 oz Pineapple rum
▫️.75 Luxardo aperitivo
▫️.75 oz Pineapple juice
▫️.5 oz lime juice
▫️.25 oz maple syrup
▫️Shake ingredients with ice for 10 seconds. Pour over 🧊and garnish with lime and #luxardo cherry
